index_terms: DEPARTMENT OF CONSTRUCTION AND LAND USE
summary: AN ORDINANCE setting fees for the Department of Construction and Land Use for reviewing and processing of applications for certain City permits, environmental analyses, inspections, related actions of other City departments, and other activities; creating and adding a new subtitle to Title 22 of the Seattle Municipal Code, repealing Seattle Municipal Code Chapter 22.900, and repealing or amending parts of Chapter 21.24.
